overview: I'm so excited the holidays are right around the corner and I finally get to see my aunt. Daddy's been getting things ready and hasn't had much time for me. I need some alone time with daddy before everyone gets here. I found him working on the kitchen and figured he couldn't say no. I teased and sucked his cock and straddled him right there on the floor. I came pretty quickly and then daddy bent me over the sink. Then I finished him off with my mouth. I hope we can find time like this when everyone's here. This was probably the wildest holiday ever. Not only did I get a bit of time with Daddy, but he tag teamed me with Uncle Jack. Then Daddy stuffed his sister and she wound up pregnant. That's going to make for an even more exciting Christmas I bet, especially if Aunt Skye is showing by then. XOXO Anneliese
title: Family Traditions 2
